Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Headmare Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bug you in\Nthe teachers' lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it OK if I miss class?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm. You can make\Nit up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll be\Ngone for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A week!? In the middle\Nof the semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is everything\Nall right, Smolder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's been\Nhaving a hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,since I left for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home\Nand check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a really sweet guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other dragons\Ncan be kinda rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say sweet guy and\Ndragon in the same sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's sorta\Nlike you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear about\Nyour brother, Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.61,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Dragonlands are really\Nfar for you to go by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not sure about you\Nmissing so much class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What if she got\Nschool credit for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like a... Kindness\Nfield trip! I'll go with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! The Dragonlord is way\Ntoo busy for personal problems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's baby-dragon-\Nhatching season.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby-dragon-hatching season!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] All those cute little\Nsnouts poking out of those
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,adorable little shells?\NTeeny tiny twitchy tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go too..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you are the perfect pony\Nto lead a kindness field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Fine. But I'm going to\Nexpect a full report
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How many pages?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking\Nto Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.99,0:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatching season\Nsounds fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: OK, I made a list of what\Ncheers me up when I'm down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so if your brother's like\Nme, he's gonna love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do\Nfirst: the "smile" song,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the sharing circle, or\Nfriendship bracelet weaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure those\Nare the kind of things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother's gonna be into...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what {\i1}would{\i0} make\Nyour brother happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just having Spike and me\Naccept him for who he is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,will make a huge difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons who appreciate\Nhis more sensitive side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it! Showtunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no. But\Ngood try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Um, that's an\Ninteresting smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The stink of sulfur,\Nsharp rocks under my claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet\Nyour brother, Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be best\Nbuddies, I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He usually hangs out near\Nhere. I'll go try and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, do you mind\Nif I take a peek
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,at the cute\Nlittle baby eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem! I'll stay here and\Nfinish this comfort blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be like a hug
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,every time Smolder's brother\Nwraps it around himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, I'm sure he'll\Nlove it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[excited gasp]\NOh, my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, little one. I've\Ncome a long way to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know there's a\Nwhole wide world out here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting to say hello?\NDid you? Oh, did you boo? [cooing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't answer\Nyou. It's an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Dragonlord Ember,\Nhow nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you too, uh\N...which one are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The party one? Apple Dash?\NOr was that the country one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy. The one\Nwho loves creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all these.. yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT? No! None\Nof them are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching over eggs is just\Npart of the glamorous life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of a Dragonlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Then maybe\Nyou can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] I'd love to! Just\Ntell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! It's my\Nfirst time being in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad wasn't big on sharing\NDragonlord details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's.. kind of a burn\Nor be burned job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure\Nyou're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. The eggs should\Nhave hatched by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But none of them\Nhave even cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Maybe\Nthey're lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry. Auntie\NFluttershy's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Dragonlord and I are\Ngoing to do everything we can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to welcome you into this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's a thing of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [tense music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't our\Nlittle pony-friend, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's "Equestria's Official\NFriendship Ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Dragonlands" to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not little.\NI had the molt, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, runt's got wings!\NI'm {\i1}so{\i0} impressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a...\Nbaby blanket to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a baby blanket!\NIt's a... comfort blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww... Did your pony\Npals make it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with friendship and gumdrops?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the way, knitting is\Na lot harder than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out the baby\Nblanket, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot harder\Nthan it looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Got your bwankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, the little baby crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet he broke a claw\Nand everything! Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back! That's\Nfor my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know laugh-fire is\Ndangerous! It can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Garble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it scalin', bra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better get out of here\Nbefore your brother shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Garble isn't very nice\Nto sensitive dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Garble\NIS my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with\Nthat, ponyboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh..!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed you, bro! We got\Na lot of fun to catch up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no lava\Ndiving at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck getting\NGarble to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Yeah, he's been so\Nweird since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding, and\Nmoping around...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, guys. I learned\Nat Twilight's school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ganging up on each other isn't\Nhalf as cool as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, Pony school made you soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try me and find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulp] Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Let's get lava\Ndiving! Whaddya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Better stay here, shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lava might ruin your\Nblankie-wankie...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the wimp tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have\Nsomedragon to dunk! Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! Only gonna warn you\Nonce. Spike's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You mess with him,\Nyou mess with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he came here to\Nhang out with YOU, Garble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, how sweet...! Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go do dragon stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Garble can have fun\Nwith his new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not having fun!\NAnd he's not my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah just ignore them, GarGar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder! Not in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's OK to\Nhave a nickname!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I'm\Ncalled Spikey Wikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You're\Nadmitting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not hanging\Nout with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a chance, Garble. You\Nguys have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine. Race you to the Lava Pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I thought you said\Nyour brother was sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All the tough guy\Nstuff is just an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a big marshmallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Not seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe a\Nburned marshmallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoky on the outside,\Nbut squishy inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He just needs friends who\Ncan appreciate that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not\Nchanging your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,about helping me\Ncheer him up, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? 'Course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Lava jumping, just\Nlike old times, huh GarGar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Just like old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for one little,\N{\i1}annoying{\i0} thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Scales away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in! The lava's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya know, whenever I'm\Nfeeling a little down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it always helps if I do\Nsomething with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we jump together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooh. Spike? You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. I know there must be something\Nworse than lava up your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ah ah ahchoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,CANNON BALL!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! [splash]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo! Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops..!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,SWALLOWING lava. Swallowing\Nlava is definitely worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they all lived\Nhappily ever after!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to come out, little ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'd like a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might be\Nencouraging them to stay in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons aren't much for\Ntouchy-feely stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! Why are\Nthe eggs shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Are they finally hatching?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish. They've been\Ndoing that for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it means something.\NBut it's probably not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this. Red velvet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Guaranteed to brighten\Nanycreature's spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you,\Nbut a change of scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,always turns my\Nfrown upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,AAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the bigger dragon.\NI will be the bigger dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the bigger dragon.\NI will be the bigger dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes just hearing what\Nsomeone appreciates about you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,can make you feel\Nbetter about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I think\Nit's really nice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're trying\Nto cheer up GarGar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Smolder.\NMy turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how you always\Nlet everycreature know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,how you're feeling, GarGar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ONLY SMOLDER GETS\NTO CALL ME THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for\Nspeaking your truth...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,More fresh lava, comin' up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, NEW activity. Who wants\Nto make vision boards?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Garble! Smolder! Surf's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let ME show you how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll.. catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Spike! There\Nyou are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For a land that's\Nall rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this place is surprisingly\Neasy to get lost in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the baby dragons doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The eggs won't hatch!\NThey just keep shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to think the\Ndragons are too scared
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to come out. I was\Nhoping you could help...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...If you're not too busy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,cheering up Smolder's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance. Smolder's\Nbrother is GARBLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that cheers him\Nup is to make me miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike! Wanna\Nplay lava ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! But that's\Nnot a very nice game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nearly got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. I mean, leave my\Nfriend alone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike came all this\Nway to cheer up Garble,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which was a very\Nkind thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, do you need\Ncheering up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Garble?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did somedragon hurt\Nyour wittle feewings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't know what\Nshe's talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's the one who's gonna cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,HEY! Are we lava\Nsurfing or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh yeah! Yeah! Let's go\Nhang with a REAL dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a pony wanna-be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I see what I\Ncan do about the eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and you cheer up Garble. At\Nleast he listens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Garble. You're\Ndealing with Fluttershy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's packing a whole\Nlifetime of kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Koochie koochie koo.\NKoochie koochie koo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,koochie! Koochie koochie\Nkoo. [angry] I said Koochie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Uh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] SPIKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be doing\Nwhatever it is you do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,at Twilight's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish. It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. These eggs\Nreally do look scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, aren't the hatching\Ngrounds supposed to be hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh of course! There's a lake\Nof molten lava under them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the\Neggs are laid here;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the heat makes them hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the\Neggs are shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause they're\Nafraid. They're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! But what\Nhappened to the lava?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Garble? Smolder? Is\Nany dragon there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [drumming] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Are those...\Nbongo drums?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire, dragon, wig and wagon...\NFeelin' like I be saggin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [drumming] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragin' lava, balaclava ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fresh lava coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered where that\Nlava was coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be draining it\Nfrom the underground lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put that rock back! Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, Dragonlord Ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been\Nremoving these boulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A while..?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It made our lava pools\Nso nice and warm-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's supposed to be\Nheating the EGGS!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they'll never hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Dragonlord Ember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put the lava back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Here you go, lava! Aw come\Non! Don't you have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's liquidy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it works that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The hatching grounds can't be the\Nonly warm place in the Dragonlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be somewhere\Nelse we can take the eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how fragile\Nthose things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way we'll be able to\Nmove them all safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr! YOU! Go and bring\Nall the dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to the hatching grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to make\Nthe heat ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing\Nsneaking around here, Pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaking? It looks to me like\Nthe only one sneaking around
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is you, Garble. Why didn't\Nyou tell me you were a poet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Words, rhythm, sometimes{\i0}\N{\i1} rhyme. Weird punctu-ation. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure sounds like poetry to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, GarGar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy won't think you're\Nsoft for being a poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither would anydragon\Nwho was your real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. OK, fine. But I'm not a\Nflowery namby pamby poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a beat poet...dig?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally feel you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you better not tell\Nmy friends about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But...why? If I was a poet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd want to share my\Ncreations with everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one Garble\Nwill perform for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't written any\Npoetry since I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's been so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I NEED to create! But if the\Nother dragons ever found out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this junk, they'd\Nmake fun of me. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you pick on Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To make your friends\Nthink you're tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. You've been\Npicking on Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh. Only when you're not looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I didn't pick on Spike,\Nthey'd just pick on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And he is kind of a weakling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmph! I'll have you know Spike\Nis STRONGER than you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Any day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. That\Nlittle cupcake-making,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,blanket-cuddling\Npony-dragon? Gimmie a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] First of all, there's nothing\Nwrong with being a pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Second, Spike isn't\Nafraid to be who he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you...\Nor anycreature thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's real strength... Not\Nlike somedragons I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For a pony without a horn,\Nshe's sure got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all\Nover for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need your\Nhelp! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ordered everydragon\Nto warm up the eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but they still won't hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nelse we can try!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give up! There's got\Nto be something we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout we wrap the eggs\Nin a bunch of baby blankets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Heheh! Yeah! The wimp can knit\N'em up real quick-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it! That laugh-fire\Ncould burn someponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn! Good idea, Spikey Wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eggs. Come. Burst\Ninto that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Break through\Nshells that... bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Break free. Explore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuck between rock\Nand... {\i1}hard place{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom. Come. Don't be shy.\NLook those others in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stake your claim.\NDon't stop, just do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the one and only.. you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-Huh!? Their laugh-fire is so hot,\Nit's hatching the eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to light. Proud to be.\NOpen up! Bam! Be... FREE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, GarGar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You performed in front\Nof other dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. And it was SUPER-LAME.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of weakling\Nwrites poetry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero of the\NDragonlands, that's who!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Garble saved our eggs\Nbecause he was strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to be who he is, whether\Nyou liked it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up thinking it was OK\Nto make fun of differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But my friends have taught\Nme to celebrate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And from now on, in my kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that's exactly what we will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't\Nmind, can you teach me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,how to write poetry like\Nthat? It's pretty cool.
